Cp in lateral view (Fig. 
2A, B
) with posterior extremity more broadly rounded than anterior one, dorsal margin broadly rounded, ventral margin weakly concave, almost straight. Maximum height situated at mid-length. Valves distinctly asymmetrical, with LV overlapping RV along anterior and posterior margins with flanges (Fig. 
